&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.frim.gov.my/?page_id=9414"&gt;Shorea resinosa : Another jigsaw puzzle in the sky&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
